    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/material_layer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130265&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=510\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/material_layer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130265&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"555\" data-width=\"978\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644604\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_layer.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"98a89b89-ac27-4342-a389-e73fa6d0b380\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/material_layer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130265&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=978&amp;height=555 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/material_layer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433130265&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=510 1x\"></span><p><br/></p><p>You can find out all the details of PxrSurface and its layerable parameters by visiting the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661411\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pixar Surface Materials</a>.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>For the easiest way to create a simple layered material, go to the RenderMan Menu and choose Create Material and select Pxr Layered Surface. We will create and network a layered material in the MAT pane.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"rfh_materialLayersCreation.png\" width=\"882\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/rfh_materialLayersCreation.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=644\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/rfh_materialLayersCreation.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"644\" data-width=\"648\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644577\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_materialLayersCreation.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9ed73dff-9855-4d96-85bd-f2982639732e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/rfh_materialLayersCreation.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=644 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/rfh_materialLayersCreation.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=648&amp;height=644 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p><h3 id=\"UsingMaterialLayers-PxrLayer\">PxrLayer</h3><p>We can override the parameters in <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661415\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrSurface</a> using the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661459\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayer</a> options. </p><p>In this example, we set a green diffuse color in PxrSurface. Then we layer a PxrLayer node on top that has a cyan diffuse color. Note that one color covers the other, so we need to alter the Mixer node.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrsurface.png\" width=\"882\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/pxrsurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129691&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=518&amp;height=290\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/pxrsurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129691&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"290\" data-width=\"518\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644580\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrsurface.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"afd49839-5700-4984-b679-d4e4f7aa6366\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/pxrsurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129691&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=518&amp;height=290 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/pxrsurface.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129691&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=518&amp;height=290 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"layer1_render1.png\" width=\"882\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/Invalid%20file%20id%20-%202f415d22-cfcd-48dc-9542-5768e3d2fcf9?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129886&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=520&amp;height=290\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/Invalid%20file%20id%20-%202f415d22-cfcd-48dc-9542-5768e3d2fcf9?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129886&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"290\" data-width=\"520\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644586\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Invalid file id - 2f415d22-cfcd-48dc-9542-5768e3d2fcf9\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c3b4927b-258b-481e-a04b-712bb466ddea\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/Invalid%20file%20id%20-%202f415d22-cfcd-48dc-9542-5768e3d2fcf9?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129886&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=520&amp;height=290 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/Invalid%20file%20id%20-%202f415d22-cfcd-48dc-9542-5768e3d2fcf9?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129886&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=520&amp;height=290 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"UsingMaterialLayers-PxrLayerMixer\">PxrLayer Mixer</h3></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>We can combine layers using <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661465\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayerMixer</a>. The mixer is where we decide where and how layers are mixed using masks. Below, patterns are connected to the Mask in the Mixer.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"rfh_mskPxrLayer.png\" width=\"882\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/rfh_mskPxrLayer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=882&amp;height=617\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/rfh_mskPxrLayer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"672\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644574\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_mskPxrLayer.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"763b916a-8e9b-4411-8025-2009a16b943f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/rfh_mskPxrLayer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=672 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/rfh_mskPxrLayer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129690&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=882&amp;height=617 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/>We can layer specular, iridescence, and other illumination lobes.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"diffuselayerrender.png\" width=\"522\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/diffuselayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=291\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/diffuselayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"291\" data-width=\"522\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644571\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"diffuselayerrender.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"30341d55-f19d-4f50-bb6b-468d229ad659\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/diffuselayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=291 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/diffuselayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=291 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"speclayerrender.png\" width=\"882\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/speclayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=292\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/speclayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"292\" data-width=\"522\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644565\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"speclayerrender.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7f1c915d-d5b7-4d90-a489-73f39e890abe\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/speclayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=292 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/speclayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=292 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"iridlayerrender.png\" width=\"882\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/iridlayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=521&amp;height=294\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644545/iridlayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"294\" data-width=\"521\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644568\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"iridlayerrender.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644545\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a97d07a7-4f63-472f-bec0-86b337e2d9be\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/iridlayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=521&amp;height=294 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644545/iridlayerrender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433129444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=521&amp;height=294 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
